Myanmar. Sagaing, Htamanthi; 

Blumea htamanthii

is only known from the type collection along the branch river of Chindwin River, growing on the steep rocks near the forest from 66-366 m altitude above mean sea level, 25.4948°-25.5152°N, 95.4319°-95.5268°E in the Htamanthii Nature Reserve.
